# Ideas for RPGManager web app

## General Direction of the app

1. Greeted with a Login Screen / User Management

2. Home page will be a layout of the inventory.

   - Probably close to the same layout as a game.
   - Half the screen will be the game layout, other half block style inventory
   - inventory needs to hav filter capablity.
   - Add equipment button somewhere on homepage.

3. "Add Equipment" button will redirect to new page

   - dropdown for style of equipment (helmet, armor, gloves, boots, belt, ring, necklace)

4. Implentation of the equipment working towards.

## Questions

1. What will the UI look like?

2. How will we implement the "working towards" equipment?
